name: Rent 2 Buy
description: Car sharing and car rentals with option
overview:
Rent2Buy is a social car-sharing platform that enables people to buy the cars that they rent, if they like them. Members can share and borrow cars from people in their community with the option to make an offer on a car they really love. Sharing your car with others while it would otherwise sit idle is a great way to generate a little extra income. Borrowing a car using the Rent2Buy platform is a great way to inexpensively rent a vehicle from somebody in your area. Car-sharing on Rent2Buy is a win for both car sharers and car borrowers.

We cover insurance, verification and logistics so you can focus on what you really love – driving great cars with people who love cars like you do.”
